Definition: involving the mind or an intellectual process
Example: mental images of happy times; mental calculations; in a terrible mental state; mental suffering; free from mental defects
Synonyms: noun, cognition, mentality, PHYSICAL, involving, the, mind, or, an, intellectual, process, mental, images, of, happy, times, calculations, in, a, terrible, state, suffering, free, from, defects
Category: adj.all
